## Task 1

```elixir
bags
|> Enum.map(fn bag ->
  size = byte_size(bag)
  half = div(size, 2)

  {b1, b2} = String.split_at(bag, half)

  [MapSet.new(to_charlist(b1)), MapSet.new(to_charlist(b2))]
end)
|> Day03.count()
```

